Package: BOLD.NODE
Title: Search and Explore BOLD Dataset Releases Efficiently
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sameer", "Padhye", , "spadhye@uoguelph.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Spencer", "Monckton", , "smonckto@uoguelph.ca", role = "aut"),
    person("Dirk", "Steinke", , "dsteinke@uoguelph.ca", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides efficient tools for exploring and transforming
    Barcode of Life Data Systems (BOLD) dataset releases on local
    machines. It enables fast searching across the entire dataset and
    seamless conversion of results into formats compatible with widely
    used R packages and third-party tools.
